reviewText: This one is worth it.  Very interesting and intriguing.
It was for my wife she love it
Almost unbelievable but there it is in black and white.
What a lovely project! Farsight Institute's series "Remote Viewing the Aliens" brings us one more precious opportunity to watch the inspiring work of Dick Allgire amd Daz Smith. Don't miss it!

If you liked the previous projects from the Farsight Institute, released on Dvd, I think you will want to see this one.
The project itself is probarbly the most interesting to date, and the presentation is much better than on the previous
dvds.
